name:                instantresolve
stack:               ( -- a )
return stack:        ( -- )
string stack:        ( -- )
contexts:            stateless
category:            interpretation, dictionary

decription:          a variable, serving as flag to turn resolving of interpretative
                     forward references on. When enabled will unknown words, entered
                     at interpretation time, be resolved immediately from portlib. If
                     a word was resolved successfully, it will be executed directly
                     after, otherwise an error is reported.

example:             instantresolve on
notes:               a shortcut  +i exists for "instantresolve on"
                     a shortcut  -i exists for "instantresolve off"
